The company designs, develops, manufactures and markets aircraft and systems, providing customer support and services. Since it was founded in 1969, Embraer has delivered more than 8,000 aircraft. namedLocations.description: Florida (/ˈflɒrɪdə/ ; Spanish for "land of flowers") is the southernmost contiguous state in the United States. The state is bordered to the west by the Gulf of Mexico, to the northwest by Alabama, to the north by Georgia, to the east by the Atlantic Ocean, and to the south by the Straits of Florida. Florida is the 22nd-most extensive (65,755 sq mi or 170,300 km²), the 3rd-most populous (21,312,211 inhabitants), and the 8th-most densely populated (384.3/sq mi or 148.4/km²) of the U.S. states. Jacksonville is the most populous municipality in the state and the largest city by area in the contiguous United States. The Miami metropolitan area is Florida's most populous urban area. Tallahassee is the state's capital.

transcript.text: Hello, welcome to on print shop.
This video is about how to assign products and template to a private store.
So in this video we will see assign product to a private store, add store specific price for private store, set discounted price or markup price to store and assign template to private store.
So let's see how we can add it in admin.
Go to the admin, click on products, go to specific product, click on add button or click on action and then on edit button.
Here you can see this product is assigned to a default store and a specific store which is you can see it over here on the Medicare.
If you want to select department specific as well, then also you can click on department specific and you can select the store along with the departments.
So this was how you can create this product with the store or department specific.
Then how to add pricing just go in pricing section.
Here you can see default store price.
So right now this price is let's say for example from one to 100, the price is $2.73 per quantity.
If you want to create some other price for the store just click on Medicare and here you can see price from one to 100 quantity is $2.30 or you can change the range as well.
So all the options are available.
Now if the product which you have already created for default store and you just want to assign it to a specific store then how can you manage that F at just go in store.
So for example if we take action and go to the product section.
So here you can see all the assigned products will be visible over here and in unassigned the products which are not assigned to this specific store, you can assign those products to this store.
Once you will click on add activities button and save it, it will be assigned and this product will be visible.
Now the pricing will be matter depending on the edit section what you have taken.
Let's see if you have taken markup type as discount or markup.
So if there's a markup type as discount, what does it means?
It means your customer of this tool will get 10% discounted price from the default store price.
And markup means 10% additional price from the default store.
So if you are choosing flat 10%, that is fine.
If you want to customize it, then there is a product markup here.
Once you will assign it, you can do the custom as well for the assigned products.
So if you want to take any custom price, you can take 5%, eight percent, 7%.
That is in reference to defaults to basic price.
So till now we have seen how to add product, then how to add pricing and then how to add product directly to the store.
Now we will see how we can add templates to a specific store.
For that just go in templates section, product templates and click on add button.
Here you need to select for which store you're creating this template.
Suppose you're creating a template for yummy restaurant, just select the private stores yummy restaurant.
If there is a specific department template then you can select the department as well.
If there is for entire store you don't need to select this department.
And apart from the department if it's a customer specific then also you can select customer name as well.
So if there is any customer related to this department that will just need to put 3 letters and the customer name will auto populate.
And then rest of the things you need to just follow how you add the templates that's it.
So in that way you can assign templates and products to a specific store.
If you have any queries and concern, please connect with us at support onprintshop.com.
Thank you.
